text.tspan: MDG5.A: Maternal mortality ratio (per 100,000 live births), 1991 to 2015
Millennium Development Goal (MDG) 5.A was to reduce the global maternal mortality ratio (maternal deaths per
100,000 live births) by 75% from 1991 levels by 2015. This target was not achieved.

text.textPath: Global target: reduce by 75% (to 95 per 100,000 live births) by 2015
